<br><br>

<b>2014 December 13:    Makati Aikido Club Christmas party</b><br><br><br>


<p>All MAC members old and new, active and inactive, and our friends from other dojos and federations, are invited to our annual Christmas party this Saturday, December 13th.</p>

<p>Interested? Please send an email with subject line "MAC Christmas party" to macaikido@yahoo.com, and we'll reply to you with the venue address and street directions.</p> 

<p>Expect the festivities to begin around 9 p.m., as the practitioners will be coming from a regular training session and kyu grade exam that ends around 8 p.m.</p>			 




